%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 4881ec947a7201b43a1b37e81f58ac96, type: 3}
  m_Name: New Audible Subtitle Info
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::RedSilver2.Framework.Dialogs.AudibleSubtitleInfo
  subtitle:
    datas:
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 19
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 21
      textToDisplay: Hello? Hello hello?
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 21
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 27
      textToDisplay: Uh, I wanted to record a message for you, to help you get settled
        in on your first night.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 27
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 34
      textToDisplay: "Um, I actually worked in that office before you, I\u2019m finishing
        up my last week now as a matter of fact. "
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 34
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 42
      textToDisplay: "So, I know it can be a bit overwhelming, but I\u2019m here
        to tell you there\u2019s nothing to worry about, Uh, you\u2019ll do fine. "
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 42
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 47
      textToDisplay: "So, let\u2019s just focus on getting you through your first
        week, okay?"
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 47
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 53
      textToDisplay: "Uh, let\u2019s see, first there\u2019s an introductory greeting
        from the company, that I\u2019m supposed to read."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 53
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 56
      textToDisplay: "Uh, it\u2019s kind of a legal thing, you know. "
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 57
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 4
      textToDisplay: "Um, \u201CWelcome to Freddy Fazbear\u2019s Pizza, a magical
        place for kids and grown-ups alike, where fantasy and fun come to life. "
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 4
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 9
      textToDisplay: Fazbear Entertainment is not responsible for damage to property
        or person.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 9
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 19
      textToDisplay: "Upon discovering that damage or death has occurred, a missing
        person report will be filed within 90 days, or as soon property and premises
        have been thoroughly cleaned and bleached, and the carpets have been replaced.\u201D "
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 19
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 21
      textToDisplay: Blah blah blah.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 21
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 23
      textToDisplay: Now that might sound bad, I know.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 23
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 26
      textToDisplay: "But, there\u2019s really nothing to worry about."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 26
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 32
      textToDisplay: Uh, the animatronic characters here, do get a bit quirky at
        night, but do I blame them? No.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 33
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 38
      textToDisplay: If I were forced to sing those same stupid songs for twenty
        years and I never got a bath?
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 38
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 41
      textToDisplay: "I\u2019d probably be a bit irritable at night too."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 41
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 47
      textToDisplay: So, remember, these characters hold a special place in the hearts
        of children and we need to show them a little respect, right?
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 48
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 49
      textToDisplay: Okay.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 49
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 53
      textToDisplay: So, just be aware, the characters do tend to wander a bit.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 1
        seconds: 54
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 7
      textToDisplay: "Uh, they\u2019re left in some kind of free roaming mode at
        night, uh, something about their servos locking up if they get turned off
        for too long?"
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 3
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 8
      textToDisplay: "Uh, they used to be allowed to walk around during the day too,
        but then there was The Bite of \u201987."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 8
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 14
      textToDisplay: "Yeah. I-It\u2019s amazing that the human body can live without
        the frontal lobe, you know?"
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 14
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 16
      textToDisplay: Uh, now concerning your safety.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 16
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 28
      textToDisplay: "The only real risk to you as a night watchman here, if any,
        is the fact that these characters, uh, if they happen to see you after hours
        probably won\u2019t recognize you as a person."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 28
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 33
      textToDisplay: "They\u2019ll pr-They\u2019ll most likely see you as a metal
        endoskeleton without its costume on."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 34
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 43
      textToDisplay: "Now, since that\u2019s against the rules here at Freddy Fazbear\u2019s
        Pizza, they\u2019ll probably try to\u2026forcefully stuff you inside a Freddy
        Fazbear suit."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 43
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 52
      textToDisplay: "Um, now, that wouldn\u2019t be so bad, if the suits themselves
        weren\u2019t filled with crossbeams, wires, and animatronic devices."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 52
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 54
      textToDisplay: Especially around the facial area.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 0
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 0
        seconds: 0
      textToDisplay: So you could imagine how having your head forcefully pressed
        inside one of those could cause a bit of discomfort, and death.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 2
        seconds: 55
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 7
      textToDisplay: Uh, the only parts of you that would likely see the light of
        day again would be your eyeballs and teeth when they pop out the front of
        the mask.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 7
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 8
      textToDisplay: 'Heh. '
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 9
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 12
      textToDisplay: "Yeah, they don\u2019t tell you these things when you sign up."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 12
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 14
      textToDisplay: But hey, first day should be a breeze.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 14
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 15
      textToDisplay: "I\u2019ll chat with you tomorrow."
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 15
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 20
      textToDisplay: Uh, check those cameras, and remember to close the doors only
        if absolutely necessary.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 21
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 22
      textToDisplay: Gotta conserve power.
    - startTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 22
      endTime:
        hours: 0
        minutes: 3
        seconds: 23
      textToDisplay: Alright, good night.
    clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1123c0f9e245e7843854f01e9cd95154, type: 3}
